{"tid":1203043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥鄭若驊收恐嚇電話　若不撤修例殺全家","createTime":"2019-06-11T11:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T11:59:48.000Z","uid":111253,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e90e01eec2595381a460a3a0839cc9caa9b8d797","tid":1203043,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190611/bkn-20190611180706337-0611_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR0NTL1_fJh0ZVqVgzyhswLLmfShq--iBIF-5cIZ6R3Zq-r2fsK8OPCGAHo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190611%2Fbkn-20190611180706337-0611_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0NTL1_fJh0ZVqVgzyhswLLmfShq--iBIF-5cIZ6R3Zq-r2fsK8OPCGAHo&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=1c5121ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190611/bkn-20190611180706337-0611_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR0NTL1_fJh0ZVqVgzyhswLLmfShq--iBIF-5cIZ6R3Zq-r2fsK8OPCGAHo</a><br />\n<br />\n政府明日(12日)把修訂《逃犯條例》草案提交立法會恢復二讀。特首辦及律政司今日(11日)分別接到死亡恐嚇電話，要求24小時內撤回修例，否則燒死她們全家。<br />\n<br />\n特首辦主任陳國基指出，今日中午12時許，特首辦收到9個電話，內容均要求特首林鄭月娥於24小時內辭職，以及撤回《逃犯條例》修訂，否則將會燒死她全家，而律政司司長鄭若驊辦公室同樣收到類似電話，要求鄭若驊辭職及撤回有關修例，否則將會掟汽油彈及燒死其丈夫潘樂陶，由於語句和內容差不多，懷疑來自同一人。<br />\n<br />\n陳國基表示已經報警，官員保安安排會交由警方處理。案件已交由中區警區重案組跟進。"},{"pid":"bd7b1b1b29790936a2eed23458c401629f9ba8f0","tid":1203043,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2441e23f14c8efdf37536b168c9fa741f34fd26","tid":1203043,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JWCPBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JWCPBP.jpg&h=62a59583&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc